{"tid":101334,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Minecraft]\u001024小時休閒生存伺服器 正版有白名","createTime":"2017-01-30T17:29:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T14:27:27.000Z","uid":21749,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d17d6b1c0fa028710e5022517672b5563ac5e10e","tid":101334,"uid":21749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T17:29:47.000Z","msg":"Minecraft\u001024小時休閒生存伺服器 正版有白名<br />\n<br />\n正版限定  版本1.11.2  有白名單<br />\nSERVER SETTING:  <br />\n/spawn /sethome /home, 防紅石連閃, <br />\n防火, 防爆(CREEPER, TNT唔會炸爆野但有傷客)<br />\n<br />\n伺服器規則: <br />\n1,唔好影響到其他玩家 <br />\n2,自律 <br />\n3.大家一齊和平打機<br />\n<br />\nSERVER大方向: <br />\n細SERVER, 細有細玩,<br />\n主要玩 休閒, 平淡, 生活, 唔會裝MOD, 唔會太依賴插件,<br />\n遲下會開多個創造世界,唔會影響到生存主世界<br />\nSPAWN點隔一段長時間會轉, 但唔會離原本果個好遠<br />\nADMIN得一兩個, 同埋唔會亂搞生存世界<br />\n<br />\n主要招募對象: <br />\n對MINECRAFT有愛, 對休閒,平淡,生活有興趣既玩家<br />\n（如果想玩咩PVP/公會/RPG/MOD/SKYBLOCK個味野, 依度唔岩你）<br />\n<br />\n可以既話係POST度留GAME名, 又或者入RC:20167559有更多既資訊<br />\n<br />\n加左白名單之後, 入SERVER, 打/register 密碼 密碼, 之後打/login 密碼 就可以出發<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIP: <a href=\"http://ilovemc.hopto.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Filovemc.hopto.org&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1NibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=6d0c6415\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ilovemc.hopto.org</a>"},{"pid":"1c5f67656a7b8c17079752d4e38ab84102a53597","tid":101334,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T17:49:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f802b3929123037108563e7a5971248f3b74a4f3","tid":101334,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T17:50:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"706d159d36dabe41b464caf310f4e79905449a29","tid":101334,"uid":21749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T18:19:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://minecraft.net/en-us/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fminecraft.net%2Fen-us%2F&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1NibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=a05b42ef\" data